OL,3,CA level results beckon for a
OL,4,C'determined' generation
OL,6,FWelsh students are patiently waiting
OL,7,Fto receive their results on Thursday,
OL,8,F14 August.
OL,10,FThis group of students has faced a
OL,11,Flot: more than two years of their
OL,12,Fsecondary education affected by Covid,
OL,13,Fand more recently, strikes by their
OL,14,Fteachers, in part because of the
OL,15,Fprofession's concern about the
OL,16,Fcondition of education in Wales.
OL,18,FSam Thomas, 18, is a student from
OL,19,FBridgend. He says his generation "are
OL,20,Fquite a determined group".
