OL,4,C'determined' generation
OL,6,FHe is hoping to get the grades needed
OL,7,Fto go to the University of Bristol to
OL,8,Fstudy zoology, which would help him
OL,9,Fachieve his aspiration of becoming a
OL,10,Fresearcher in that field.
OL,12,FHe said: "We've had a lot going on but
OL,13,Fthese are our futures on the line, and
OL,14,Fwe still need to get through it, no
OL,15,Fmatter what."
OL,17,FThis year is the first time of
OL,18,Freturning to pre-pandemic marking in
OL,19,FWales, making it harder to compare
OL,20,Fthis year's results with previous
OL,21,Fyears.
