OL,3,CA level results beckon for a
OL,4,C'determined' generation
OL,6,FIn addition, comparing results between
OL,7,FUK nations is problematic because of
OL,8,Fthe different approaches to
OL,9,Fqualifications across the nations.
OL,11,FHowever, one indicator that can give a
OL,12,Fsense of how the Welsh system is
OL,13,Ffaring in comparison to other nations
OL,14,Fis the number of students going to
OL,15,Funiversity.
OL,17,FStatistics released earlier this
OL,18,Fsummer revealed the proportion of 18-
OL,19,Fyear-olds applying to go to university
OL,20,Fhas dropped.
