OL,3,CA level results beckon for a
OL,4,C'determined' generation
OL,6,FDescribing the rate as "alarming",
OL,7,FUniversities Wales found that the
OL,8,Fnumbers of students applying are at a
OL,9,F15-year low, with the gap between
OL,10,FWales and the rest of the UK at its
OL,11,Fwidest.
OL,13,FAccording to Amanda Wilkinson,
OL,14,Fdirector of Universities Wales, this
OL,15,Fcould have a lon-term economic impact
OL,16,Fbecause the industries "that will
OL,17,Fdrive our economic growth in the
OL,18,Fdecades to come" rely heavily on
OL,19,Fgraduates.
