OL,3,CA level results beckon for a
OL,4,C'determined' generation
OL,6,FWales' education secretary Lynne
OL,7,FNeagle MS told ITV Cymru News that the
OL,8,Ffigures were "worrying" and that the
OL,9,FWelsh Government is "focused" on
OL,10,Funderstanding what it can do to
OL,11,F"further increase participation".
OL,13,FIn May this year, she told the Senedd
OL,14,Fthat there is "excellence in every
OL,15,Fpart of our system, but I am
OL,16,Fabsolutely clear that we need to aim
OL,17,Fhigher".
